 231, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ogunsemilore tested positive for furosemide, a diuretic on WADA's prohibited list, in an out-of-competition doping control collected on Thursday.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The athlete has been informed of the case and has been provisionally suspended until the resolution of the matter in line with the World Anti-Doping Code and the International Olympic Committee (IOC) Anti-Doping Rules,\\\" the ITA said.\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Anti-Doping Code\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Anti-Doping_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intercollegiate_Tennis_Association\", \"score\": 0.9379669749130967, \"rank\": 0.04266524084760732, \"text\": \"ITA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intercollegiate_Tennis_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intercollegiate_Tennis_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ogunsemilore is now prevented from competing in training, coaching, or participating in any activity, during the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, a huge blow for Team Nigeria.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_wom